cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DL 

The paper proposes a novel model-based reinforcement learning algorithm that uses uncertainty estimates to improve asymptotic performance. This involves policy optimization, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm is also designed to work with deep neural networks (cs.DL) and robotics (cs.RO), which are mentioned in the abstract. Finally, the paper involves system dynamics (cs.SY), which is a subfield of control theory that deals with modeling and analyzing complex systems.
